title: AM2R - Another Metroid 2 Remake v1.2.9.1 - Windows
description:
Another Metroid 2 Remake v1.2.9.1 by DoctorM64
Release Date: May 23rd, 2017

A complete remake of Metroid 2: Return of Samus for the Game Boy, upgraded to (at least) Super Metroid-level graphics and gameplay. 

System Requirements:

Pentium III 600Mhz, 256MB RAM
150MB Hard Drive Space
Windows (or WINE)


-----------------------------------------------------------
PROJECT AM2R
v1.2.9.1

-----------------------------------------------------------

SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
- DirectX9.0 or newer installed
